overview: Two stepbrothers, played by Adam Ramzi and newcomer Jake Nicola, take their young sexy step-nephews out for a weekend away in the big city. Sexual tension grows heavy and after a sweaty session between the two stepbrothers and some sweet sexy play by the two step-cousins, the action really heats up when Uncle Bobby and Uncle Jake find out just how wild Avery really is.
title: Uncle Bobby
